text: Novokucherganovka () is a rural locality (a selo) in Starokucherganovsky Selsoviet, Narimanovsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 482 as of 2010. There are 14 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Astrakhan, 50 km from Narimanov. == References == Category:Rural localities in Narimanovsky District
title: Novokucherganovka
